<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-86-0534 </DOCNO><TEXT>Glasses of the system LiF - Li/sub 2/O - B/sub 2/O/sub 3/ are investigated.Experimental data obtained agree with the model of the glasses studied,according to which with the introduction of lithium fluoride to lithium-borateglass the B-F bonds are not formed in a noticeable quantity.</TEXT></DOC>